        <del rend="strikethrough">wretch</del></mod> Abhorred monster,<anchor xml:id="c56-0125.03"
      /></line>
    <line>cried I furiously, <milestone unit="tei:q" spanTo="#c56-0125.04"/>fiend that thou
      art</line>
    <line>the tortures of Hell are too <del rend="strikethrough">soft for thee</del><add><ptr
