          all the feelings which can arm one</add></mod></line>
    <line>He eluded <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">me easily,</add> and said – <milestone
        unit="tei:q" spanTo="#c56-0124.08"/>Be calm! I entreat</line>
    <line><del rend="triple-strike">h</del> you to hear me, before you give vent</line>
    <line>to your hatred <add resp="#pbs" place="intralinear">up</add>on my devoted head.
      Have</line>
    <line>I not suffer<del rend="cross-hatch">r</del>ed enough that you</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">should</del> wish to encrease my misery–Life</line>
    <line>although it be only an accumulation</line>
    <line>of anguish is dear to me and I will defend</line>
    <line>it remember thou hast made me more</line>
